Every unit, except mines, refineries, and characters, costs a specific number of maintenance points.  The number of points currently in our maintenance pool is displayed in the rightmost monitor above the GID. Our maintenance pool will decrease each time we build a new unit.  Maintenance points will also be lost as the result of loss of mines or refineries.  We can increase the size of our maintenance pool by building additional mines and refineries, taking control of systems with existing mines and refineries, or scrapping units that are no longer necessary to our efforts.